title: BREAKING: Nigeria's Acting Chief Justice Onnoghen speaks on Buhari's inaction - Premium Times
text: BREAKING: Nigeria's Acting Chief Justice Onnoghen speaks on Buhari's inaction - Premium Times Premium Times The Acting Chief Justice of Nigeria , Walter Onnoghen, has appealed to Nigerians not to pressure President Muhammadu Buhari into appointing him the substantive Chief Justice.
